This study is a Phase I/II trial of Tivantinib plus FOLFOX for the treatment of patients with advanced solid tumors.

 In Phase I the Maximum Tolerated Dose (MTD) will be determined; in Phase II patients with first-line metastatic GE cancer will be treated at the MTD.

 It is hypothesized that the response rate (RR) will be improved from 45% to at least 65% under this regimen.

